{"tid":551911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭《東方》控誹謗 Google就海外派票令提上訴遭駁回","createTime":"2018-02-06T05:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T08:17:13.000Z","uid":54733,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3b423a407808c4d0436ce41c403b2974980f4c84","tid":551911,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180206/large/1517893989_a2db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180206%2Flarge%2F1517893989_a2db.jpg&h=e2059907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東方報業集團有限公司、東方日報督印有限公司、太陽報督印有限公司於2015年入稟高等法院，指在Google搜尋引擎輸入「白粉報」三字，即會顯示誹謗字句。總部設於美國的Google早前申請撤銷海外派票令不果後上訴，上訴庭今頒判詞駁回上訴，指原告目前已證明案中涉及真實及重大誹謗，至於如何平衡言論自由和保護原告聲譽，應留待審訊處理。<br />\n<br />\n被告Google LLC.質疑原審法官駁回撤銷派票令申請時，將單純在網上發佈資訊，錯誤地引申成發佈已達足以構成誹謗的程度。上訴庭在判詞反駁指，原告引用Google統計數據顯示在相關時期，「白粉報」一詞每月平均被搜尋320次；Google若質疑有關搜尋是由原告有關人士故意製造，應該提出證據。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭續指，一間企業被指從事不法及不道德勾當，必然可視為有傾向對該企業造成傷害，具體有沒有傷害需在審訊時判斷。"},{"pid":"ba81e41d2b87b3b8741a98678cea42cc90e14572","tid":551911,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"遭《東方》控誹謗 Google就海外派票令提上訴遭駁回<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180206/57798611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F57798611&d=hIPhOiaFzJJfBAMIi8cg%2BcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=bcb39690\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F57798611&h=310aaaf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180206/57798611</a>"},{"pid":"a6eec00858fa93a1a1038a76869c257fe9c7fc5a","tid":551911,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"All in 東方報孽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=